metadata.description: Hatémas Painting - Rescue Rangers Area0 - converted back into real NFT pixels ◼️◼️▪️▪️ As a graphic artist Hatemás has always been fascinated by the storytelling of digital games and street art worlds. As a child of the seventies he loves the style of the early gaming era. In his work he’s in search of the beauty and the aesthetics of these forgotten places.
